--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CIVMC COMMUNITY NOTICE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This application was created for the Commonwealth nation on the CivMC
Minecraft server. CivMC is a community-run Civilization-style Minecraft
server.

Commonwealth Flag (Commonwealth_flag.png)
  The Commonwealth flag image is a community-created asset representing the
  in-game nation of Commonwealth on CivMC. The original author is unknown,
  but it is freely used within the CivMC Commonwealth community. If you are
  the original creator and wish to be credited or have concerns about its
  use, please open an issue on the project repository.

